 @param gameId Unique identifier for the game
 @param host Address of the game host
 @param timestamp Block timestamp when game was created

@notice Emitted when a player joins a game
 @param gameId Game identifier
 @param player Address of the joining player
 @param timestamp Block timestamp when player joined

@notice Emitted when the host commits a word hash
 @param gameId Game identifier
 @param commitment Hash of the word (prevents cheating)
 @param timestamp Block timestamp of commitment

@notice Emitted when a game is completed and scores are recorded
 @param gameId Game identifier
 @param host Address of the game host
 @param word The revealed word that was drawn
 @param winners Array of winner addresses
 @param scores Array of final scores for winners
 @param timestamp Block timestamp of completion

@notice Host commits a hash of the word to be drawn
 @dev Uses commit-reveal pattern to prevent cheating
 @param gameId The game identifier
 @param commitment Hash of keccak256(abi.encodePacked(word, salt))

@notice Reveals the word and records final scores
 @dev Verifies the reveal matches the commitment
 @param gameId The game identifier
 @param word The word that was drawn
 @param salt Random salt used in commitment
 @param winners Array of winner addresses
 @param scores Array of final scores corresponding to winners

@notice Gets game room details
 @param gameId The game identifier
 @return host The game host address
 @return wordCommitment The committed word hash
 @return createdAt Timestamp of game creation
 @return isActive Whether the game is active

@notice Gets the total number of wins for a player
 @param player The player address
 @return Total number of wins

